description:
Blue Protocol: Star Resonance Gameplay Preview - SHOULD You PLAY It? Is It Worth it? (Anime MMORPG)

In this Fextralife video we'll be taking a look at Blue Protocol: Star Resonance, a brand new Anime MMORPG that just launched on October 9th and was developed by Shanghai Bokura Network, and published by A PLUS Japan. The game is playable on PC and mobile devices, and is Free-to-Play.

Download the game here for FREE and support the channel: https://bpsr.onelink.me/Ijsy/3cpd5iwp
Sponsored by: A PLUS Japan

We'll talk about Gameplay, story and what sort of activities are present in the Anime MMO, including Dungeons, and World Bosses.
